'''Harrowbane''' was a [[Poison/Legends|poisonous]] weed that grew on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Randorn 2]]. The native [[Mizx]] considered harrowbane a sacred [[Plant/Legends|plant]] and would construct barriers of it to keep away dangerous [[ibliton]]s. The weed had an [[Acid/Legends|acidic]] burning effect on ibliton tentacles.

